---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About CycleWise">
  <div class="page-wrap prose" style="max-width:680px;">
    <h1>About CycleWise</h1>
    <p>CycleWise was built for one reason: most relationship friction that happens during the month isn't random. It follows a pattern. That pattern is the menstrual cycle.</p>
    <p>Hormones drive energy, emotion, libido, appetite, and communication style — and they shift predictably across four phases every month. Most women know this about themselves. Most of their partners don't have a clue.</p>
    <p>CycleWise bridges that gap. It gives partners a simple calendar and daily briefing so they can stop guessing and start showing up with the right energy at the right time.</p>
    <h2>Privacy first</h2>
    <p>All cycle data is stored in your browser's local storage. It never leaves your device. We don't have a database of cycles. We can't see your data because we don't receive it.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions or feedback: <a href="mailto:hello@cyclewise.app">hello@cyclewise.app</a></p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h1 { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .prose h2 { margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .prose p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .prose a { color: var(--pink); }
</style>
